definitely the formation of the Kingdom of Brunei Darussalam, which is a cool name for a country.

The past 2 years was when the country introduced VAT, an unpopular tax, as a means to reduce the countries debt on top of the oil revenue.

Ongoing since the last 4 years is the Infrastructure road construction along the sides of Jalan Mukim Saik, Berakas.

Another momentous occassion was the recent presidential elections when the inaugural President of Brunei Darussalam is formally elected by the Parliament of Brunei.

I hope you found this useful in increasing your knowledge of Brunei.
